{"TopicId":222802,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal portrait arrangment.","CreatedByName":"DaveLChgo","CreatedById":179012,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-08T05:51:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DaveLChgo","CreatedById":179012,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-08T05:51:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood morning all!\u00A0 \u00A0 Kinda bugs me that the portraits don\u0027t seem to follow logic.\u00A0 Two issues here.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nCrew portrait arrangement\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nStowaways\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen building an Apollo style craft in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E. The crew manager shows the 5 seats.\u00A0 CM 3 seats above the LM 2 seats.\u00A0 Thats fine and is as expected.\u00A0 But I\u0027m always getting a stowaway Kerbal in the LM.\u00A0 Come to think of it when I had a craft with a CM / LM / Rover the stowaway would always be in the Rover.\u00A0 So maybe the stowaway gets inserted into the bottom most seat.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut back to this example.\u00A0 In the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E we have the Apollo style craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#2e3035;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022LdFvcZg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022294.35\u0022 height=\u0022989\u0022 width=\u0022336\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/LdFvcZg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe crew manager shows the stowaway, Shercas.\u003Cbr\u003E\nNext we add crew to the CM (Mk1-3)\u00A0 They are\u00A0Herbree, Ludel and Doodoly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#2e3035;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HL0Uzdt.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022145.65\u0022 height=\u0022485\u0022 width=\u0022333\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/HL0Uzdt.png\u0022\u003E\u00A0 \u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#2e3035;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u002248rnHXh.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022170.59\u0022 height=\u0022522\u0022 width=\u0022306\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/48rnHXh.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen launching this Apollo style craft. \u00A0You will see 3 portraits... occupied (Shercas), empty, mechjeb.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#2e3035;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00224i9296M.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002245.75\u0022 height=\u0022471\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/4i9296M.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe next row is three portraits all mechjeb.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#2e3035;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00227AZPunY.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002245.92\u0022 height=\u0022489\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/7AZPunY.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe last row is 3 portaits... occupied (Herbree, Ludel, Doodoly)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#2e3035;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00222hN203J.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002246.00\u0022 height=\u0022492\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://imgur.com/2hN203J.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere are the asks...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nToggle the mech portraits off.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGroup the portraits by part.\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nEstablish a hierarchy. \u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe CM portraits shouldn\u0027t be at the bottom in the example above.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for listening!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-01-08T06:00:19Z\u0022 title=\u002201/08/2024 06:00  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jan 8\u0022\u003EJanuary 8\u003C/time\u003E by DaveLChgo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Poppa Wheelie","CreatedById":218525,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-08T17:07:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224356993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022222802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221704693112\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179012\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DaveLChgo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, DaveLChgo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere are the asks...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI support all of your asks.\u00A0 In addition:\u00A0 I want to be able to drag and drop the portraits into any order I want.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}